MAINT: Remove unused code in ratios_to_colors

mcolors.rgb2hex requires as tuple of 3 colors, these
tuples come from an array/list i.e [[], [], [], ...].
These nested values were later gauranteed and so no need
to the exception.

Remove utils.isinf

mizani had not yet shipped a version that used this method,
and it does not seem necessary. The method was introduced in
a supposed fix for a plotnine bug, upon careful review this
was unnecessary.

MAINT: Refactor brewer_pal

Lookup the number in colours in the various colorbrewer palettes.
Hard coding the palette sizes often had me checking to see if
colorbrewer had changed them.

MAINT: Remove unused case from datetime_trans

When the datetime_trans.transform was written `date2num`
from matplotlib did not support `np.datetime64` so we had
a special case for it. Now `date2num` has `np.datetime64`
support.
Improve boxcox_trans for small p & add clear tests

MAINT: Remove dead code in scale.train

Commit a3eb047 improved the handling of nan values
and the code branch we have removed useless. This
used multitype_sort to sort discrete values of
multiple types e.g. numbers and strings.

The helper function multitype_sort will remain, it is used
upstream in plotnine.
